title: Wanna Become a Dad or a Boyfriend
description:
Childhood friends Park Suhyuk and Yu Seoha secretly like each other, but are too shy to show it.
However, at a gathering where they're now considered as adults, Seoha begins the preparetions to live on her own. When all of a sudden, Seoha's mom, Oh Jieun, suddenly tries to seduce Suhyuk...
author: Saetmi
